awd_titl_txt: Travel Funds for U.S. Attendees to the Tenth World          Conference on Earthquake Engineering to be held in Madrid,  Spain on July 19-24, 1992
awd_abstract_narration: This project will provide travel                                                support for a U.S. Delegation of                                                highly qualified earthquake                                                     engineering researchers to attend                                               and participate in the 10th World                                               Conference on Earthquake Engineering                                            (10WCEE), July 19-24. 1992, in                                                  Madrid, Spain.  As recognized                                                   leaders in the field of earthquake                                              engineering, U.S. investigators                                                 supported by this project will                                                  present results of their current                                                research work at this important                                                 international forum.
org_div_long_name: Division of Civil, Mechanical, and Manufacturing Innovation
